short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Enable ClickOnce support in Google Chrome.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Breez ClickOnce 4C enables ClickOnce support in Google Chrome.
It is required to be able to launch any Windows Forms or Windows Presentation Foundation application that is based on Microsoft's ClickOnce technology.
